snippet.title: The Super 1-1 Challenge Trailer (FPS Super Mario Bros. Prototype)
snippet.description:
Download here: https://sean-noonan.itch.io/super 

Some commentary: Okay, I'm pretty much done with The Super 1-1 Challenge now. I've got a couple of little quality of life features to finish off, but it's basically done! Hope everyone enjoys this little experiment! :)

Trailer music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C1Y_d_Lhp60

Want to find out more? Join the Discord: http://discord.noonan.design/

Web: http://noonan.design
Twitter: http://twitter.com/SeanNoonan
Tumblr: http://seannoonan.tumblr.com

#SuperMario #MarioFPS #UE4
